  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1278630">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1278630/" class="title-link">“幸福是自己体会的”</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1278630"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2163820/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2163820-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2163820/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">potter</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-01-10"
      class="main-meta">2008-01-10 22:05:14</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1278630_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  觉得这本书写的亮点在“不幸福的原因”，这种原因是藏在心底的，不易被人察觉的。当孜孜以求“幸福之路”的时候，有没有想到过也许追求的恰恰是相反。“如果方向不正确，再努力又有什么用呢”。如果多避免些不幸福的原因，幸福就要简单很多。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
